{"tid":577535,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"榮升上市公司主席　袁彌明坐擁7億身家　買內衣冧夫","createTime":"2018-03-01T23:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T13:07:30.000Z","uid":81228,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"60b21c02bd5facc8dba9a9c8471ed0cc6ee6c015","tid":577535,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T23:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/03/02/110304/wnep110p01a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F110304%2Fwnep110p01a.jpg&h=9a2fae1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n低調行超市 ■做過藝人、議員，現榮升做上市公司主席嘅袁彌明，當晚淡妝戴帽低調行超市。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/03/02/110304/wnep110p01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F110304%2Fwnep110p01b.jpg&h=14a0a9fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夫婦拍住上 ■2月12日，Erica和丈夫兼非執行董事林雨陽拖手主持上市儀式。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/03/02/110304/wnep110p01c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F110304%2Fwnep110p01c.jpg&h=d80aa963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有車接送 ■買完嘢，袁彌明行去後門，司機就揸住架用公司登記嘅紅色Tesla嚟接。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/03/02/110304/wnep110p01d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F110304%2Fwnep110p01d.jpg&h=d2cfa07a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n捐去排隊 ■為咗快幾秒，袁彌明踎低捐去快速排隊畀錢。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/03/02/110304/wnep110p01e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F110304%2Fwnep110p01e.jpg&h=1e65a0e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n掃海膽 ■人妻買咗兩盒大海膽，唔知係佢鍾意食，定同丈夫開心share呢？<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/03/02/110304/wnep110p01f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F110304%2Fwnep110p01f.jpg&h=90eaa707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n犀利人妻 ■袁彌明14年12月與公民黨創黨成員林雨陽結婚，索人妻婚後無意生B。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/03/02/110304/wnep110p01g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F110304%2Fwnep110p01g.jpg&h=5c40a799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n辭任主席 ■16年9月，人民力量主席袁彌明宣佈辭任，由陳志全（左）暫代主席。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/03/02/110304/wnep110p01h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F110304%2Fwnep110p01h.jpg&h=8560b535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n家人支持 ■「彌明生活百貨」去年9月於將軍澳開設第9間分店，丈夫林雨陽、奶奶、母親齊到場支持。<br />\n<br />\n37歲前港姐、人民力量前主席袁彌明（Erica），今年2月攀升為上市公司主席！佢創辦嘅彌明生活百貨（8473）上月喺創業板掛牌，股價持續飆升，截至周四（3月1日）收市價0.81元，公司市值9億，Erica持股75%，身家跳升至逾6.8億元。新任主席於新春其間偕夫蜜遊後返港，見人妻淡妝行逛時代廣場買咗兩盒海膽醫肚。是日亮點係Erica手挽一袋意大利高級內衣，唔通人妻打算忙碌過後，同丈夫林雨陽增進吓閨房樂？！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>袁彌明05年參選港姐，僅得個豬肉獎「旅遊大使」獎，同屆冠軍係</strong><br />\n<br />\n口依家做咗幸福媽媽嘅葉翠翠，亞季分別係陸詩韻和林莉。兩年後，佢和無線決裂，接吓水着job，又開始喺YouTube拍美容片教化妝、護膚，09年轉型開辦袁彌明生活百貨，專賣自己親身試過嘅美容產品。進擊嘅Erica亦由商界跳入政界， 加入政黨「人民力量」同參選立法會議員後，就一改穿衣風格，套裝上陣力sell專業形象。16年9月，佢辭去人民力量主席一職，唔知係咪為做女強人鋪路呢！之後舖頭愈開愈多，至今有9間分店。身兼公司主席及行政總裁嘅袁彌明於上市日仲透露希望三年內開多5間分店口添！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>連開5間店</strong><br />\n<br />\n農曆新年後，Erica隻股表現向好，較招股價0.27元升兩倍，本周四收市價0.81，袁彌明持股75%或8.4億股計，身家狂飆至6.8億元。犀利人妻日前同丈夫外遊度歲後返港，獨自往銅鑼灣時代廣場city'super買壽司。戴帽嘅低調人妻手挽Hermes garden party手袋，買咗袋意大利高級品牌LA PERLA內衣，然後喺超市揀生蝦壽司和兩盒海膽。之後，Erica連人帶車仔捐入去快速排隊畀錢，再上地面等架紅色Tesla嚟接載返家。<br />\n<br />\n採訪 : 梁志明<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/ent/650028/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fent%2F650028%2F&d=m8so%2FOR4F3kCltcsHZh%2B5LZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=195803e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fent%2F650028%2F&h=c4fcd22f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/ent/650028/</a>"},{"pid":"d6b7baf9df1399ca54fcbf79464e01892bc7d4d7","tid":577535,"uid":34562,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T23:58:45.000Z","msg":"佢都算叻"},{"pid":"34e674d25a3becd6adf71012d76e51089a34221f","tid":577535,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T00:24:54.000Z","msg":"必廚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bef76f5a797b9cc6bbb4ce8eaa5351fc37400c","tid":577535,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T00:26:57.000Z","msg":"佢老公就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aadbe354e76d10b068ecb82a37308dfcbc0f2a3","tid":577535,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T00:28:28.000Z","msg":"佢幾時做過議員"},{"pid":"3f025bfc00a8f6c8d2232fcea3c8dd1f4d40f9b0","tid":577535,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T00:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6851d71945327dab4c8cd01f9d90ee1382f7c7a3","tid":577535,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T00:32:04.000Z","msg":"乜都玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbef45587e045e90abd45c6e8620a0dc9d28ba6","tid":577535,"uid":114027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T01:17:12.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係靠嫁有錢人發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a4d5f06be0b5d9c2c86470544c061a239f4543","tid":577535,"uid":44513,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2